span class=\"source\" style=\"display:block;\"><i style=\"float:left;\">原文</i>&nbsp; \n                <a class=\"cut cut70\" href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/articles/goto?id=vquaei\" style=\"display:inline-block;\">http://mobilesyrup.com/2015/05/17/top-canadian-mobile-stories-from-the-past-week-52/</a>\n            </span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"article_body\" id=\"nei\">\n            <div> \n <p> <img src=\"http://img0.tuicool.com/rqIRraU.jpg\" class=\"alignCenter\" /> </p> \n <div itemprop=\"articleBody\"> \n  <div> \n   <div> \n    <img src=\"http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/32f88abe87eebc19b55223edb560e731?s=62&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F1.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D62\" height=\"62\" width=\"62\" /> \n   </div> \n   <div> \n    <p> <a href=\"http://www.mobilesyrup.com\" title=\"Visit Ian Hardy’s website\" rel=\"nofollow,noindex\">Ian Hardy</a> </p> \n    <p>May 17, 2015 7:19am</p> \n   </div> \n  </div> \n  <p>Every week we bring you the latest in Canadian mobile news. Listed below is a quick overview of the top stories from the past seven days.</p> \n  <div> \n   <p> – Apple Watch review [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – MTS customers can now make mobile payments [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – Samsung Galaxy S6 and S6 edge will receive Android 5.1 in June [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – Canadian telcos have to work much harder to please customers [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – Apple says HomeKit will launch in June [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – The iPhone 6 Plus, six months later [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – LG G4 launching in Canada on June 19th [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – Telus, Videotron big winners in 2500Mhz spectrum auction [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – Canadian mobile users spend more time on Facebook than Twitter [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – CRTC warns about telemarketers claiming to represent the DNCL [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – Thalmic’s Myo Gesture Control Armband now available at Best Buy [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – CSIS and other enforcement agencies can wiretap Hangouts [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – Samsung Galaxy S6 vs. Galaxy Note 4 [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – White BlackBerry Leap now available in Canada [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – W|W: The Wearable Weekly – Dark sides [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – BlackBerry Leap review [Read here] </p> \n   <p> – SyrupCast 41: Promises of G4-reatness [Listen here] </p> \n  </div> \n </div> \n</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"article_social\">\n        <div class=\"article_like\">\n                <button class=\"btn btn-large btn-like\" id=\"my_like2\" data_id=\"vquaei\">\n                    <i class=\"icon-heart-empty\"></i>\n                    赞一个\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"btn btn-large btn-fav liked\" id=\"my_like\" data_id=\"vquaei\">\n                    <i class=\"icon-star-empty\"></i>\n                    收 藏\n                </button>\n        </div>\n        </div>\n           <div id=\"site_articles\">\n              <div class=\"article-part-title\">\n                <span>推荐文章</span>\n              </div>\n          <ul class=\"side_article_list\">\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    1.<a href=\"/articles/rUR73yU\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"iPhone 6S And Galaxy Note 5 Leaks Reveal Early Release Dates\">\n                    iPhone 6S And Galaxy Note 5 Leaks Reveal Early Release Dates\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    2.<a href=\"/articles/buArmqu\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Tablet with the new Remix OS 1.5 will be launched soon\">\n                    Tablet with the new Remix OS 1.5 will be launched soon\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    3.<a href=\"/articles/vUb2QrR\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Microsoft Word, PowerPoint and Excel hit Android phones in beta\">\n                    Microsoft Word, PowerPoint and Excel hit Android phones in beta\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    4.<a href=\"/articles/nyqQbyR\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Droid Turbo gets three new metallic accent colors from Verizon, available starting May 28\">\n                    Droid Turbo gets three new metallic accent colors from Verizon,..\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    5.<a href=\"/articles/b6reYvN\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Google is the king of mobility\">\n                    Google is the king of mobility\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    6.<a href=\"/articles/uQfIJvV\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Apple can&#x27;t quit making expensive docks for your iPhone\">\n                    Apple can&#x27;t quit making expensive docks for your iPhone\n                </a>\n                </li>\n         </ul>\n        </div>\n\n        <div id=\"kan_articles\"></div>\n        <div id=\"article_weibo\" style=\"display:none;\">\n            <div class=\'article-part-title\'>\n                <span>相关微博</span>\n                <sub>\n                    <a href=\"/articles/weibo_list/vquaei\" target=\"_blank\">(<i id=\"weibo_num\"></i>)</a> \n               </sub>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"related-weibo-list\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"comments\">\n    <div class=\"comments-area\">\n    <div class=\"comments-header\">\n        <h5>我来评几句</h5>\n        <div class=\"alert comment-alert alert-error\" style=\"display:none;\">\n            错误\n        </div>\n            <textarea cols=\"60\" rows=\"5\" id=\"comment-body\" placeholder=\"请输入评论内容...\"></textarea>\n            <span class=\"btn btn-medium btn-submit\"  id=\"comment-submit\">登录后评论</span>\n        <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-l