             <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/mags/design\">设计匠艺</a></li> \n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/articles/weekly\">一周拾遗</a></li>                  \n                </ul>\n              </li>\n              \n               <li class=\"dropdown  \">\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">更多 <b class=\"caret\"></b></a>\n                <ul class=\"dropdown-menu\">\n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/bbs\">讨论区</a></li>  \n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/about\">关于我们</a></li>                 \n                </ul>\n              </li>\n              \n              </ul>\n            <form class=\"navbar-search pull-left\" action=\"http://www.tuicool.com/search\">\n              <input type=\"text\" class=\"search-query span2\" name=\"kw\" placeholder=\"搜索\">\n            </form>\n            <ul class=\"nav pull-right\">\n                <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/login\">登录</a></li>\n            </ul>\n          </nav>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n  </div>   \n</div>\n  <div id =\"flash_container\" class=\"noPrint\">    \n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"container-fluid\">  \n    <div class=\"frd_pos\">\n    <div class=\"row-fluid\" style=\"margin-top: 15px\">\n        <div>\n            <script type=\"text/javascript\">BAIDU_CLB_fillSlot(\"1076478\");</script>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid article_row_fluid\">\n    <div class=\"span8 contant article_detail_bg\">\n        <h1>Meizu M1 Note Launches In India May 20th</h1>\n        <div class=\"article_meta\">\n            <span class=\"timestamp\">时间&nbsp;2015-05-18 18:24:56\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"from\">\n                <i class=\"icon-globe\"></i>\n                    <a class=\"cut cut28 from\" href=\"/sites/FfE3Ar\" target=\"_blank\">Geeky-Gadgets\n                    </a>\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"source\" style=\"display:block;\"><i style=\"float:left;\">原文</i>&nbsp; \n                <a class=\"cut cut70\" href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/articles/goto?id=73Q7Zf\" style=\"display:inline-block;\">http://www.geeky-gadgets.com/meizu-m1-note-launches-in-india-may-20th-18-05-2015/</a>\n            </span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"article_body\" id=\"nei\">\n            <div itemprop=\"text\"> \n <p> <img src=\"http://img0.tuicool.com/2QJJ73E.jpg\" class=\"alignCenter\" /> </p> \n <p>The Meizu M1 Note will launch in India this week, the handset will go on sale this Wednesday the 20th of May and it will be sold through Amazon in India.</p> \n <p>The handset features a 5 inch display with a HD resolution of 1280 x 720 pixels and processing is provided by a quad core processor.</p> \n <p>Powering the Meizu Mi Note is a MediaTek MT6732 processor and the handset also comes with 1GB of RAM and 8GB of included storage.</p> \n <p>The built in storage can be expanded by a further 128GB thanks to a microSD card slot and the handset also features a 2500 mAh battery and front and rear facing cameras.</p> \n <p>On the front of the Mi Note is a 5 megapixel camera for video calls and selfies and on the back of the handset there is a 13 megapixel camera for photos and videos. Other specifications include Bluetooth, WiFi and 4G LTE, there are also dual SIM card slots.</p> \n <p> Source <a href=\"http://thenextweb.com/mobile/2015/05/18/meizus-m1-note-is-the-chinese-companys-first-smartphone-to-go-on-sale-in-india/?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+TheNextWeb+%28The+Next+Web+All+Stories%29\" rel=\"nofollow,noindex\">TNW</a> </p> \n</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"article_social\">\n        <div class=\"article_like\">\n                <button class=\"btn btn-large btn-like\" id=\"my_like2\" data_id=\"73Q7Zf\">\n                    <i class=\"icon-heart-empty\"></i>\n                    赞一个\n                </button>\n                <bu