www.tuicool.com/mags\">编程狂人</a></li>\n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/mags/design\">设计匠艺</a></li> \n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/articles/weekly\">一周拾遗</a></li>                  \n                </ul>\n              </li>\n              \n               <li class=\"dropdown  \">\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">更多 <b class=\"caret\"></b></a>\n                <ul class=\"dropdown-menu\">\n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/bbs\">讨论区</a></li>  \n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/about\">关于我们</a></li>                 \n                </ul>\n              </li>\n              \n              </ul>\n            <form class=\"navbar-search pull-left\" action=\"http://www.tuicool.com/search\">\n              <input type=\"text\" class=\"search-query span2\" name=\"kw\" placeholder=\"搜索\">\n            </form>\n            <ul class=\"nav pull-right\">\n                <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/login\">登录</a></li>\n            </ul>\n          </nav>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n  </div>   \n</div>\n  <div id =\"flash_container\" class=\"noPrint\">    \n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"container-fluid\">  \n    <div class=\"frd_pos\">\n    <div class=\"row-fluid\" style=\"margin-top: 15px\">\n        <div>\n            <script type=\"text/javascript\">BAIDU_CLB_fillSlot(\"1076478\");</script>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid article_row_fluid\">\n    <div class=\"span8 contant article_detail_bg\">\n        <h1>Spotify wants to turn your Starbucks barista into a DJ</h1>\n        <div class=\"article_meta\">\n            <span class=\"timestamp\">时间&nbsp;2015-05-19 06:04:37\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"from\">\n                <i class=\"icon-globe\"></i>\n                    <a class=\"cut cut28 from\" href=\"/sites/7JRVvq\" target=\"_blank\">Mashable\n                    </a>\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"source\" style=\"display:block;\"><i style=\"float:left;\">原文</i>&nbsp; \n                <a class=\"cut cut70\" href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/articles/goto?id=UF3Evmj\" style=\"display:inline-block;\">http://mashable.com/2015/05/18/spotify-starbucks-partnership/</a>\n            </span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"article_body\" id=\"nei\">\n            <div>\n  <p>Now your barista is also a DJ.</p>\n  <p>Spotify and Starbucks have announced a multi-year partnership to put the music streaming service in stores across the U.S., Canada and the United Kingdom.</p>\n  <p>The agreement will give each Starbucks employee a new perk — a Spotify Premium subscription — that they can use to tweak the in-store playlists. Those playlists will also be available to Spotify users.</p>\n\n    <p>\nSee also:      <a href=\"http://mashable.com/2013/10/06/spotify-music-economy/\" rel=\"nofollow,noindex\">How Spotify Engineered the New Music Economy</a>\n    </p>\n    <p>Spotify users will also be able to get &quot;Stars and Currency&quot; as part of the My Starbucks Rewards loyalty program.</p>\n  <p>“For over forty years, music has played a vital role in Starbucks Third Place experience – inspiring our partners and customers in unexpected ways that have helped to shape the global pop culture. And we are delighted and honored to bring Spotify directly to our customers,” said Howard Schultz, CEO of Starbucks in a press release.</p>\n  <p>\nThe deal is one of the largest corporate partnerships every announced by Spotify and comes as the company has lost momentum in the past couple years. Its recent financials showed that    <a href=\"http://mashable.com/2015/05/09/spotify-lost-a-ton-of-money-last-year-and-heres-exactly-how-much/\" rel=\"nofollow,noindex\">the company lost $197 million</a>\nin 2014 despite bring in more revenue and topping    <a href=\"http://mashable.com/2015/01/12/spotify-15-million-60-million/\" rel=\"nofollow,noindex\">15 million subscribers</a>\n.  </p>\n  <p>\nSpotify also hasa deal with Uber in which premium users can play music during their rides.  </p>\n  <p>\nSpotifyrecently announced that it had tripled its losses in two years.  </p>\n</div>\n\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"article_social\">\n        <div class=\"article_like\">\n                <button class=\"btn btn-large btn-like\" id=\"my_like2\" data_id=\"UF3Evmj\">\n                    <i class=\"icon-heart-empty\"></i>\n                    赞一个\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"btn btn-large btn-fav liked\" id=\"my_like\" data_id=\"UF3Evmj\">\n                    <i class=\"icon-star-empty\"></i>\n                    收 藏\n                </button>\n        </div>\n        </div>\n           <div id=\"site_articles\">\n              <div class=\"article-part-title\">\n                <span>推荐文章</span>\n              </div>\n          <ul class=\"side_article_list\">\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    1.<a href=\"/articles/IN3ieaa\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"‘Not for attribution’ quotes are tech reporting’s dirty little secret\">\n                    ‘Not for attribution’ quotes are tech reporting’s dirty litt..\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    2.<a href=\"/articles/u6FJvam\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Pinterest Adds Audience Targeting, CPA Model To Promoted Pins\">\n                    Pinterest Adds Audience Targeting, CPA Model To Promoted Pins\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    3.<a href=\"/articles/eEVzemm\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"New Browser Extension Decides How Trustworthy You Are\">\n                    New Browser Extension Decides How Trustworthy You Are\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    4.<a href=\"/articles/uymAbeV\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"You can now watch the &#x27;Netflix for pirated movies&#x27; right from your web browser\">\n                    You can now watch the &#x27;Netflix for pirated movies&#x27; right from y..\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    5.<a href=\"/articles/UVFVVj2\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"iSpot.tv Raises $21.9M To Track The Online Impact Of TV Advertising\">\n                    iSpot.tv Raises $21.9M To Track The Online Impact Of TV Adverti..\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    6.<a href=\"/articles/Y3mYniV\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"This was Sony Music&#x27;s contract with Spotify\">\n                    This was Sony Music&#x27;s contract with Spotify\n                </a>\n                </li>\n         </ul>\n        </div>\n\n        <div id=\"kan_articles\"></div>\n        <div id=\"article_weibo\" style=\"display:none;\">\n            <div class=\'article-part-title\'>\n                <span>相关微博</span>\n                <sub>\n                    <a href=\"/articles/weibo_list/UF3Evmj\" target=\"_blank\">(<i id=\"weibo_num\"></i>)</a> \n               </sub>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"related-weibo-list\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"comments\">\n    <div class=\"comments-area\">\n    <div class=\"comments-header\">\n        <h5>我来评几句</h5>\n        <div class=\"alert comment-alert alert-error\" style=\"display:none;\">\n            错误\n        </div>\n            <textarea cols=\"60\" rows=\"5\" id=\"comment-body\" placeholder=\"请输入评论内容...\"></textarea>\n            <span class=\"btn btn-medium btn-submit\"  id=\"comment-submit\">登录后评论</span>\n        <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-left:10px;\">\n            已发表评论数(<span class=\"comment_cnt\"></span>)\n        </p>\n    </div>\n    <div