gs\">编程狂人</a></li>\n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/mags/design\">设计匠艺</a></li> \n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/articles/weekly\">一周拾遗</a></li>                  \n                </ul>\n              </li>\n              \n               <li class=\"dropdown  \">\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">更多 <b class=\"caret\"></b></a>\n                <ul class=\"dropdown-menu\">\n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/bbs\">讨论区</a></li>  \n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/about\">关于我们</a></li>                 \n                </ul>\n              </li>\n              \n              </ul>\n            <form class=\"navbar-search pull-left\" action=\"http://www.tuicool.com/search\">\n              <input type=\"text\" class=\"search-query span2\" name=\"kw\" placeholder=\"搜索\">\n            </form>\n            <ul class=\"nav pull-right\">\n                <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/login\">登录</a></li>\n            </ul>\n          </nav>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n  </div>   \n</div>\n  <div id =\"flash_container\" class=\"noPrint\">    \n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"container-fluid\">  \n    <div class=\"frd_pos\">\n    <div class=\"row-fluid\" style=\"margin-top: 15px\">\n        <div>\n            <script type=\"text/javascript\">BAIDU_CLB_fillSlot(\"1076478\");</script>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid article_row_fluid\">\n    <div class=\"span8 contant article_detail_bg\">\n        <h1>Huawei produced Nexus smartphone based on Mate 8</h1>\n        <div class=\"article_meta\">\n            <span class=\"timestamp\">时间&nbsp;2015-05-17 09:43:47\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"from\">\n                <i class=\"icon-globe\"></i>\n                    <a class=\"cut cut28 from\" href=\"/sites/B3uuMv\" target=\"_blank\">talkandroid\n                    </a>\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"source\" style=\"display:block;\"><i style=\"float:left;\">原文</i>&nbsp; \n                <a class=\"cut cut70\" href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/articles/goto?id=QB3EBbY\" style=\"display:inline-block;\">http://www.talkandroid.com/249000-huawei-produced-nexus-smartphone-based-on-mate-8/</a>\n            </span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"article_body\" id=\"nei\">\n            <div> \n <p> <img src=\"http://img2.tuicool.com/MV3eE3f.jpg\" class=\"alignCenter\" /> </p> \n <p>Sources in China claim that the forthcoming Huawei-produced Google Nexus smartphone will be based on a prototype of the manufacturer’s Mate 8 smartphone. Previous leaks have suggested the next Nexus smartphone will have a 5.7-inch 2K display which would be consistent with the Mate 8 from Huawei. </p> \n <p>However, the Mate 8 is slated to be powered by Huawei’s in-house produced Kirin 930 processor. The next Nexus is believed to be equipped with a Snapdragon 810 processor despite the controversy swirling around that chip. This newest source indicates the Nexus device could be powered by a Kirin 950 chip, which is likely Huawei’s next generation following the Kirin 930.</p> \n <p>Other hardware details are still unclear, especially the construction of the device. If based on the Mate 8, the new Nexus device should give the impression of a high quality smartphone, possibly employing a metal chassis and lots of glass.</p> \n <div> \n  <p> source: <a href=\"http://news.mydrivers.com/1/429/429732.htm\" rel=\"nofollow,noindex\" target=\"_blank\">MyDrivers.net</a> </p> \n  <p> via: <a href=\"http://www.gizmochina.com/2015/05/16/upcoming-nexus-smartphone-developed-from-huawei-mate-8-prototype/\" rel=\"nofollow,noindex\" target=\"_blank\">GizmoChina</a> </p> \n </div> \n <p> <a href=\"https://plus.google.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.talkandroid.com%2F249000-huawei-produced-nexus-smartphone-based-on-mate-8%2F\" title=\"Share on Google+\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow,noindex\"> <i></i> </a> <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.talkandroid.com%2F249000-huawei-produced-nexus-smartphone-based-on-mate-8%2F\" title=\"Share on Facebook\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow,noindex\"> <i></i> </a> </p> \n</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"article_social\">\n        <div class=\"article_like\">\n                <button class=\"btn btn-large btn-like\" id=\"my_like2\" data_id=\"QB3EBbY\">\n                    <i class=\"icon-heart-empty\"></i>\n                    赞一个\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"btn btn-large btn-fav liked\" id=\"my_like\" data_id=\"QB3EBbY\">\n                    <i class=\"icon-star-empty\"></i>\n                    收 藏\n                </button>\n        </div>\n        </div>\n           <div id=\"site_articles\">\n              <div class=\"article-part-title\">\n                <span>推荐文章</span>\n              </div>\n          <ul class=\"side_article_list\">\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    1.<a href=\"/articles/rUR73yU\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"iPhone 6S And Galaxy Note 5 Leaks Reveal Early Release Dates\">\n                    iPhone 6S And Galaxy Note 5 Leaks Reveal Early Release Dates\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    2.<a href=\"/articles/buArmqu\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Tablet with the new Remix OS 1.5 will be launched soon\">\n                    Tablet with the new Remix OS 1.5 will be launched soon\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    3.<a href=\"/articles/vUb2QrR\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Microsoft Word, PowerPoint and Excel hit Android phones in beta\">\n                    Microsoft Word, PowerPoint and Excel hit Android phones in beta\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_li