     <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/mags/design\">设计匠艺</a></li> \n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/articles/weekly\">一周拾遗</a></li>                  \n                </ul>\n              </li>\n              \n               <li class=\"dropdown  \">\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">更多 <b class=\"caret\"></b></a>\n                <ul class=\"dropdown-menu\">\n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/bbs\">讨论区</a></li>  \n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/about\">关于我们</a></li>                 \n                </ul>\n              </li>\n              \n              </ul>\n            <form class=\"navbar-search pull-left\" action=\"http://www.tuicool.com/search\">\n              <input type=\"text\" class=\"search-query span2\" name=\"kw\" placeholder=\"搜索\">\n            </form>\n            <ul class=\"nav pull-right\">\n                <li><a href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/login\">登录</a></li>\n            </ul>\n          </nav>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n  </div>   \n</div>\n  <div id =\"flash_container\" class=\"noPrint\">    \n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"container-fluid\">  \n    <div class=\"frd_pos\">\n    <div class=\"row-fluid\" style=\"margin-top: 15px\">\n        <div>\n            <script type=\"text/javascript\">BAIDU_CLB_fillSlot(\"1076478\");</script>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid article_row_fluid\">\n    <div class=\"span8 contant article_detail_bg\">\n        <h1>Lily, the robotic flying drone camera</h1>\n        <div class=\"article_meta\">\n            <span class=\"timestamp\">时间&nbsp;2015-05-17 14:25:36\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"from\">\n                <i class=\"icon-globe\"></i>\n                    <a class=\"cut cut28 from\" href=\"/sites/aiUbUn\" target=\"_blank\">YugaTech\n                    </a>\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"source\" style=\"display:block;\"><i style=\"float:left;\">原文</i>&nbsp; \n                <a class=\"cut cut70\" href=\"http://www.tuicool.com/articles/goto?id=Arma6vn\" style=\"display:inline-block;\">http://www.yugatech.com/photography/lily-the-robotic-flying-drone-camera/</a>\n            </span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"article_body\" id=\"nei\">\n            <div> \n <p> We’ve already seen a lot of drones in the past few years but this one called <strong>Lily</strong> is the dubbed as the world’s first throw-and-shoot camera. </p> \n <p> <img src=\"http://img0.tuicool.com/bYzuYn7.jpg\" class=\"alignCenter\" /> </p> \n <p>The Lily looks like your typical quadcopter with a built-in camera but this time, there’s no need to navigate it manually. The Lily will follow the owner using a tracking device which can be worn on the wrist.</p> \n <p> <img src=\"http://img0.tuicool.com/Mvu6BfJ.jpg\" class=\"alignCenter\" /> </p> \n <p>The built-in camera has a 12-megapixel sensor, shoots full HD 1080p at 60fps and can take slow-mo 120fps shots at 720p.</p> \n <p>The battery will last up to 20 minutes on a single full charge and automatically follows the user up to a speed of 40kmph. The Lily is also waterproof so you don’t have to worry about accidentally dropping it in water or operating it under ehavy rain.</p> \n <p> <img src=\"http://img0.tuicool.com/baiUJjY.jpg\" class=\"alignCenter\" /> </p> \n <p>You can check out the demo video here:</p> \n <p>The Lily will be available by February 2016 for $999 but if you pre-order now, they can give it for $499 only.</p> \n <p> { <a href=\"https://www.lily.camera/\" rel=\"nofollow,noindex\">source</a> , <a href=\"http://petapixel.com/2015/05/12/lily-is-the-worlds-first-throw-and-shoot-camera/\" rel=\"nofollow,noindex\">via</a> } </p> \n</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"article_social\">\n        <div class=\"article_like\">\n                <button class=\"btn btn-large btn-like\" id=\"my_like2\" data_id=\"Arma6vn\">\n                    <i class=\"icon-heart-empty\"></i>\n                    赞一个\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"btn btn-large btn-fav liked\" id=\"my_like\" data_id=\"Arma6vn\">\n                    <i class=\"icon-star-empty\"></i>\n                    收 藏\n                </button>\n        </div>\n        </div>\n           <div id=\"site_articles\">\n              <div class=\"article-part-title\">\n                <span>推荐文章</span>\n              </div>\n          <ul class=\"side_article_list\">\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    1.<a href=\"/articles/nM7buiu\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"So Over The “Overly-Retouched” Argument\">\n                    So Over The “Overly-Retouched” Argument\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    2.<a href=\"/articles/ZBbemq\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Fujifilm X-T10 Camera Promises Better Action Shots\">\n                    Fujifilm X-T10 Camera Promises Better Action Shots\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    3.<a href=\"/articles/qEfQby\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Deal: Kingston memory cards and other accessories are up to 74% off on Amazon\">\n                    Deal: Kingston memory cards and other accessories are up to 74%..\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    4.<a href=\"/articles/InyENby\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"The new Olympus 7-14mm PRO lens got reviewed by Robin Wong!\">\n                    The new Olympus 7-14mm PRO lens got reviewed by Robin Wong!\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    5.<a href=\"/articles/eAJnMnj\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Canon sharpens its image with 5DS R (hands-on)\">\n                    Canon sharpens its image with 5DS R (hands-on)\n                </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"side_article_list_item\">\n                    6.<a href=\"/articles/jiYfqiN\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"This One Photo: Australia’s aurora captured in space\">\n                    This One Photo: Australia’s aurora captured in space\n                </a>\n                </li>\n         </ul>\n        </div>\n\n        <div id=\"kan_articles\"></div>\n        <div id=\"article_weibo\" style=\"display:none;\">\n            <div class=\'article-part-title\'>\n                <span>相关微博</span>\n                <sub>\n                    <a href=\"/articles/weibo_list/Arma6vn\" target=\"_blank\">(<i id=\"weibo_num\"></i>)</a> \n               </sub>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"related-weibo-list\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"comments\">\n    <div class=\"comments-area\">\n    <div class=\"comments-header\">\n        <h5>我来评几句</h5>\n        <div class=\"alert comment-alert alert-error\" style=\"display:none;\">\n            错误\n        </div>\n            <textarea cols=\"60\" rows=\"5\" id=\"comment-body\" placeholder=\"请输入评论内容...\"></textarea>\n            <span class=\"btn btn-medium btn-submit\"  id=\"comment-submit\">登录后评论</span>\n        <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-left:10px;\">\n            已发表评论数(<span class=\"comment_cnt\"></span>)\n        </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"comments-list\">\n        <div class=\"empty-cmts alert alert-success\" style=\"display:none;\">\n            没有更多评论了^^\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"more-comments\" style=\"display:none;\">\n        <a href=\"\">更多评论</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"load-fail\" style=\"display:none;\">\n        评论加载失败，<a href=\"javascript:reload_comments(\'Arma6vn\',1,0,-1);\">重新加载</a>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n    </div>\n         <div class=\"span4 article_right_side\">\n            \n            <div class=\"right_top\">\n    <div clas