-576\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-576\"><a title=\"Tools\" href=\"http://designimag.com/category/tools/\"><i class=\"fa-wrench fa\"></i><span class=\"fontawesome-text\"> Tools</span></a></li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-743\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-743\"><a title=\"Tutorials\" href=\"http://designimag.com/category/tutorials/\"><i class=\"fa-text-width fa\"></i><span class=\"fontawesome-text\"> Tutorials</span></a></li>\n</ul></div>						\r\n					</nav>\r\n\r\n				<!-- 	This file is part of a WordPress theme for sale at ThemeForest.net.\r\n						See: http://themeforest.net/item/breeze-personal-minimalist-wordpress-blog-theme/5423780\r\n						Copyright 2013 Bluthemes 	-->\r\n			\r\n			</div>\r\n		</header><!-- #masthead .site-header -->\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"main\" class=\"container\">\r\n		<div id=\"primary\" class=\"row right_side\">\r\n<div class=\"above_content col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12\"><div class=\"\"><p><script type=\"text/javascript\">\n    google_ad_client = \"ca-pub-4058525277387314\";\n    google_ad_slot = \"8142562387\";\n    google_ad_width = 728;\n    google_ad_height = 15;\n</script><br />\n<!-- DIM TextAd --><br />\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script></p>\n</div></div>		<div id=\"content\" class=\"image-comment-on col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-8 \" role=\"main\"> 					<article id=\"post-69\" class=\"post-69 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-tips\">		<div class=\"entry-image\" style=\"\">				<div class=\"image-comment\" rel=\"bookmark\" data-href=\"http://designimag.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/why-marry-web-developers4.jpg\">\r\n					<img width=\"750\" height=\"455\" src=\"http://designimag.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/why-marry-web-developers4.jpg\" class=\"attachment-original wp-post-image\" alt=\"why-marry-web-developers\" />				</div>		</div>						<div class=\"entry-container box clearfix  \">\r\n\r\n							<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n								<div class=\"post-title\">\r\n									<h1 class=\"entry-title\">Why you should Marry a Web Developer</h1>\r\n									<div class=\"post-meta\">\r\n										<ul>\r\n	<li><time class=\"entry-date updated\" datetime=\"2015-05-18T19:33:55+00:00\">May 18, 2015</time></li>\r\n	<li class=\"divider\">/</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://designimag.com/category/tips/\" title=\"View all posts in Tips\">Tips</a> </li>	<li class=\"divider\">/</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://designimag.com/why-you-should-marry-a-web-developer/#comments\">2 Comments</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n									</div>\r\n								</div> <p>Having crushes, liking somebody or having friends of opposite gender is not a big deal, but then real struggle pops up when you are planning to settle down. Whom to marry, who is the right guy for you are big question of all the single people. Ain&#8217;t it?</p>\n<p>Meeting the right man/woman who you feel is the person you would want to spend the rest of your life is not as easy as it sounds to be. When you come across such a person and decide to marry still there are doubts and different type of questions that keep hovering in the mind.</p>\n<p>Geeks, nerds, developers and tech savvy are a group of people that girls used to avoid in the past for the fact that they found them boring. However, over the course of years and with the fast paced development in the web world, the scenario has changed. If you have a developer friend who you are falling for or want to settle with but wondering if it&#8217;s the right thing to do, then my answer would be yes, go for it! Why? Here are some really good reasons why you should get married to the developer. Check them out!</p>\n<h3>1. Developers are Extremely Thoughtful</h3>\n<p>Talk about holiday plans or gift ideas you will be amazed with the thoughtful ideas of your developer hubby. Not only this, you will get to learn how unexpectedly your hubby would remember every single detail of the travel, and special days.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"http://designimag.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/why-marry-web-developers.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-896\" src=\"http://designimag.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/why-marry-web-developers.jpg\" alt=\"why-marry-web-developers\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" /></a></p>\n<h3>2. They are Low Maintenance</h3>\n<p>By low maintenance I mean to say you will not have to go for expensive gifts for the special days for your developer hubby. Gift him anything of his interest or something he likes to have, or anything related to his work and he will be more than happy. They are not like after designer stuff, infact they think very less of actually how they look or go for expensive clothes. You know how geeks are!</p>\n<h3>3. They are Full of Creative Ideas</h3>\n<p>You might argue over developers being creative as their job is more related to codes and bugs, but then the way they see things and the ideas they come up with are quite different from others. The way they do/see things comes up with ideas of doing things are far different from others.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"http://designimag.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/why-marry-web-developers1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-897\" src=\"http://designimag.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/why-marry-web-developers1.jpg\" alt=\"why-marry-web-developers\" width=\"600\" height=\"392\" /></a></p>\n<h3>4. You get your Personal Developer for Life!</h3>\n<p>Wink, wink! This is one obvious benefit of getting married to a web developer. You all know debugging takes much more time than fixing any other household problem. Your developer hubby will say no to fixing the faucet or solve electricity issue, but will help you debug your computer anytime of the day and that too happily. Its a bonus besides other good reasons to give developers a chance to be your life partner.</p>\n<h3>5. They are Friendly</h3>\n<p>Developers might not have many friends, but then the ones they have been amazing. This doesn&#8217;t mean developers do not get well with people. They easily get along with people and are quite friendly.</p>\n<h3>6. Small Things don&#8217;t Bother Them Much</h3>\n<p>The issue that might appear big to you unless you discuss with your nerdy hubby will suddenly look like nothing big and fussy happened. This is for the fact that small things don&#8217;t move the geeks, infact they know how to handle things without panicking or bothering too much. In short, they are problem-solving people.</p>\n<h3>7. They are Humble</h3>\n<p>Geeks, developers or nerdy people as you call them never fail to appreciate the great work, smart ideas and anything/anyone they like. They tend to give true opinions and are humble enough to learn new things from others, respects relationships and other things in life</p>\n<h3>8. Fast Learners</h3>\n<p>Geeks, developers are quite fast in grasping things. They can quickly research, understand things, be it professional, related to the world, ideas and much more.</p>\n<h3>9. They are Focused</h3>\n<p>Have you ever seen a developer while working? They are so much focused and unaware of what&#8217;s happening around them that they sometimes forget to sip a cup of coffee placed right in front of them. In life too, developers are quite focused and they know what they want in life.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"http://designimag.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/why-marry-web-developers2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-898\" src=\"http://designimag.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/why-marry-web-developers2.jpg\" alt=\"why-marry-web-developers\" width=\"600\" height=\"302\" /></a></p>\n<h3>10. They are Loyal</h3>\n<p>Who doesn&#8217;t want a loyal husband? Marrying the developer lessens down the chances of you falling into the situation to hire a detective to spy. He will be loyal to you like his work.</p>\n<h3>11. Needless to Mention; They are Successful</h3>\n<p>Last but not the least, we all know, web developers don&#8217;t have the dearth of work. For a passionate web developer, there are innumerable projects. I am not at all trying to convince you that people in other jobs/fields are not financially stable, but the probability of being financially unstable for a developer is quite less.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"http://designimag.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/why-marry-web-developers3.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-899\" src=\"http://designimag.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/why-marry-web-developers3.jpg\" alt=\"why-marry-web-developers\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you have a nerdy or a developer friend around whom you really like, then I guess the above listed reasons are convincing enough to give that geeky guy a chance and take a chance.</p>\n<p>Developers might appear to be boring, but they are definitely not! Exceptions are always there, but the fact remains that developers, nerds come in different packages and are simply lovely people to be with. Infact, this nerdy person in your life is sure to make the second phase of your life much more interesting and worth living for!</p>\n<div class=\"wp-subscribe-single wp-subscribe-after-content\">            \n            <div class=\"wp-subscribe no-name-field\" id=\"wp-subscribe\" style=\"background: #828282;\">\n                <h4 class=\"title\" style=\"color: #dd3333;\">Subscribe to our Newsletter</h4>\n                <p class=\"text\" style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Get useful resources, tips, freebies and inspiration dosage by subscribing to our free email newsletter.</p>\n                \n                                    \n                    <form action=\"http://designimag.com/why-you-should-marry-a-web-d